pix over the net yet. Gomen. Let us know if that is OK and we'll give you
the website addresses for DL. Arigato. Sayonara from us both-Keiman and Kei.
PS-we finally found out the name of the river on Rurouni Kenshin from the
kenshingamesurf.com site. It is the Sumida-gawa River. Arigato for all your
help hazu.-K&K
